org.researchstack.backbone.answerformat

Class FormAnswerFormat

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.researchstack.backbone.answerformat.AnswerFormat
      • org.researchstack.backbone.answerformat.FormAnswerFormat
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    java.io.Serializable

    public class FormAnswerFormat
extends AnswerFormat
    AnswerFormat indicating that the QuestionStep is a form step. This lets the layout know that it needs to use the individual QuestionSteps inside the form step to build the ui and validate answers.
